Take out rice(Basmati)
take out measuring cups
take out pan
pour 2 cups of water into pan
add 1x tp of oil
add 1x tp of salt
turn on stove top
put pan on stovetop(that is on)
heat water until boiling point
add rice
check water level until its 1/4 of the amount originally poured into pan
lower heat to low
check pan every 5 mins
wash and rinse measuring cup
put away rice bag
move rice pan to a stovetop that is off
enjoy! yum yum 
